{"tid":2147102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"埃及政府指TikTok內的影片腐敗 拘留多名女姓","createTime":"2020-08-09T04:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T05:49:58.000Z","uid":56115,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfaffbce10a552ed8444ec2dd8109eda9dfff25","tid":2147102,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:30:44.000Z","msg":"埃及當局拘留了一些在TikTok上發佈自己跳舞影片的年輕女性，稱她們 &quot;腐敗&quot;。據指，當局表示不允許女性在保守伊斯蘭的社區中發佈影片，一些女性因此被判處兩年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n據當地報紙等消息，今年4月，檢察官拘留了20歲的女大學生Hanine Hosam，她在TikTok上擁有130萬Fans。在影片中，Hanine穿著完全沒有露出皮膚的長袖衣服跳舞，並曾呼籲女性觀眾通過發佈影片獲得收入。自4月以來，已有5名女性因與TikTok有關而被拘留，其中一名女性發佈了一段自己身著輕裝的影片。 (共同社)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sankei.com/world/news/200809/wor2008090002-n1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sankei.com%2Fworld%2Fnews%2F200809%2Fwor2008090002-n1.html&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=ddbc13f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sankei.com/world/news/200809/wor2008090002-n1.html</a>"},{"pid":"8bc3faaecc3a47d7fa4161b081e856bbed9b9883","tid":2147102,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1fc1020d9b1cb26bce0b2a38065bb7c5cc49e32","tid":2147102,"uid":92299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8bc3faaecc3a47d7fa4161b081e856bbed9b9883","tid":2147102,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"唔係唔比用, 係唔比女人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a07c3530293a02322252006f1c75af3b5353917","tid":2147102,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02